d support an independent view of risk is a founding principle of validus and underpins the ‘validus view of risk’  since our formation validus has consistently invested in building a team of thought leaders and expert practitioners focused on the ability to better model and better interpret the risks we face the validus group is composed of validus re talbot underwriting western world insurance group and alphacat managers listed on the new york stock exchange our business maintains a clear focus on a robust underwriting discipline that is central for our continued success through our four diversified yet complementary businesses we are able to offer our clients the benefits of scale as well as greater efficiencies through platform integration our global network has grown to  offices with over  employees in all major regions worldwide which means we can offer services that integrate macrotrends alongside local understanding meeting our clients needs quick facts composed of validus re talbot western world and alphacat  profitable in all years of operation  through    offices with over  employees in all major regions worldwide   find an office asia pacific australia bermuda europe latin america middle east  north africa north america investor toolkit latest annual report latest form k latest form q latest earnings release latest financial supplement latest investor presentation contact form × name email phone enquiry send form close a gallery image title lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit debitis ab iure doloremque cum corrupti libero molestias voluptate optio expedita commodi omnis perferendis repudiandae asperiores accusantium tempora laboriosam quasi minima iste lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit eveniet laudantium debitis cum libero provident sequi x error invalid input validus  validus holdings menu about us about us back executive teams executive teams back validus holdings western world insurance group talbot underwritin